quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  79,1,"By those [angels] who extract with violence{1}",footnotes:1:1
  79,2,"And [by] those who remove with ease{1}",footnotes:1:1
  79,3,"And [by] those who glide [as if] swimming{1}",footnotes:1:1
  79,4,"And those who race each other in a race{1}",footnotes:1:1
  79,5,"And those who arrange [each] matter,{1}",footnotes:1:1
  79,6,"On the Day the blast [of the Horn] will convulse [creation],"
  79,7,"There will follow it the subsequent [one]."
  79,8,"Hearts,{1} that Day, will tremble,",footnotes:1:1
  79,9,"Their eyes{1} humbled.",footnotes:1:1
  79,10,"They are [presently] saying, "Will we indeed be returned to [our] former state [of life]?"